ilter object.

Possible filters: `$eq`, `$gt`, `$gte`, `$in`, `$lt`, `$lte`, `$ne`, `$startsWith`.

For a detailed list of supported filters, see [sorting and filtering for labels](https://dev.wix.com/api/rest/contacts/labels/sort-and-filter).

Example: `{ "filter": {
"displayName": {
"$startsWith": "Referral"
}
}
}`
